<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>-<span class="c5"> الناشي:</span> عبد الله بن محمد <span class="c4">[٤٣٩٨]</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
